OL,3,CBelfast Trust culture report says
OL,4,Ccardiac unit poses risk to patient
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FPersonal conflict within the cardiac
OL,8,Fsurgery team at the Royal Victoria
OL,9,FHospital continues to pose a risk to
OL,10,Fpatient safety and service delivery an
OL,11,Findependent report has found.
OL,13,FThe report found that due a
OL,14,Ffundamental breakdown in relationships
OL,15,Fbetween some of the Consultant Cardiac
OL,16,FSurgeons, "there is little trust
OL,17,Fbetween them and consequently there is
OL,18,Fan ongoing risk to service delivery
OL,19,Fand patient safety."
