OL,7,FIt continued: "There is still
OL,8,Fsignificant risk associated with the
OL,9,Fdysfunctional team dynamics within the
OL,10,FCardiac Surgical Team."
OL,12,FThe report was commissioned by the
OL,13,Fhealth minister after UTV exclusively
OL,14,Frevealed that a culture of poor
OL,15,Fbehaviour by some heart surgeons at
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland's cardiac surgery
OL,17,Funit led to a "significant risk to
OL,18,Fpatient safety."
