OL,7,FThe medical unit that has been under
OL,8,Fscrutiny for its workplace culture
OL,9,Fwith allegations of bullying and poor
OL,10,Fbehaviour overshadowing its life
OL,11,Fsaving work.
OL,13,FA personal feud within the unit
OL,14,Fescalated to the point that a small
OL,15,Fnumber of surgeons refused to go into
OL,16,Fthe workplace and some operations had
OL,17,Fto be cancelled.
