OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FThe reports authors Dr Jennifer Hill
OL,8,Fand Peter McBride said there were
OL,9,Fmultiple examples of excellent
OL,10,Fbehaviours within the Trust, but also
OL,11,Fflagged up that there were some other
OL,12,Fareas where behaviours had fallen
OL,13,Fshort of what was expected.
OL,15,FHealth minister Mike Nesbitt said he
OL,16,Fhe hoped that recommendations made
OL,17,Fwithin the report will help the
OL,18,FBelfast Trust move forward.
