OL,7,F"I'm very grateful to Peter McBride
OL,8,Fand Jennifer Hill for completing that
OL,9,Fwork. They've done the diagnostics and
OL,10,Fhave come up with 10 recommendations,
OL,11,Fmostly for the trust.
OL,13,F"I'm delighted that Tony Stevens,
OL,14,Fformerly of the Northern Trust, will
OL,15,Fgo in to help with the implementation
OL,16,Fof that. We will also, as a
OL,17,FDepartment, look at the broader
OL,18,Flearnings for the Health and Social
OL,19,FCare system, and those learnings will
OL,20,Fbe disseminated to the other trusts."
