OL,7,FIn a written statement to MLAs
OL,8,FMinister Nesbitt said he "I remain
OL,9,Fcommitted to ensuring that all staff
OL,11,Facross the HSC system experience work
OL,12,Fenvironments where they are valued and
OL,13,Fsupported on a daily basis and where
OL,14,Fthe enduring culture is one of
OL,15,Fopenness, transparency and respect."
OL,17,FBut health committee members believe
OL,18,Fseveral questions remain unaswered.
