OL,7,FDUP MLA Diane Dodds said: "I do stress
OL,8,Fthat the issues of a toxic culture, of
OL,9,Fbad behavior, and of bullying from
OL,10,Fmanagement is not just confined to the
OL,11,FCardiac Surgical Unit.
OL,13,F"It is a widespread trust issue. I've
OL,14,Fspoken to many doctors across all
OL,15,Fdisciplines within the Trust who
OL,16,Fexpressed real concern about
OL,17,Fmanagement of their problems."
