OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"The report notes that 'there is still
OL,8,Fsignificant risk associated with the
OL,9,Fdysfunctional team dynamics within the
OL,10,Fcardiac surgical team.' The fact that
OL,11,Fthis remains an issue raises serious
OL,12,Fquestions about what actions the Trust
OL,13,Fhas taken so far, and what more will
OL,14,Fnow be done to ensure patient safety.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
