OL,3,CBelfast Trust culture report says
OL,4,Ccardiac unit poses risk to patient
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"It is welcome that 17 per cent of
OL,8,FTrust staff - almost 3,500 people -
OL,9,Ftook part in the review. That level of
OL,10,Fengagement demonstrates a clear
OL,11,Fcommitment among staff to deliver
OL,12,Fmeaningful change and to help shape a
OL,13,Fbetter culture moving forward.
OL,15,F"However, it also highlights the scale
OL,16,Fof the problem across the
OL,17,Forganisation, and the Minister cannot
OL,18,Fignore the level of concern that
OL,19,Fexists.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
