OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1761175134
OL,3,CBelfast Trust culture report says
OL,4,Ccardiac unit poses risk to patient
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"The report also reveals that 61 per
OL,8,Fcent of respondents lack confidence in
OL,9,Fhow the Trust would handle a report of
OL,10,Fconcern, and that many staff remain
OL,11,Freluctant to report inappropriate
OL,12,Fbehaviour for fear that nothing will
OL,13,Fbe done. Such high levels of
OL,14,Fdissatisfaction in Trust processes is
OL,15,Fsimply unacceptable.
OL,17,F"I have been raising these issues for
OL,18,Fsome time and have spoken to
OL,19,Fclinicians across various specialisms
OL,20,Fwho share these frustrations.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
