OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1761175134
OL,3,CBelfast Trust culture report says
OL,4,Ccardiac unit poses risk to patient
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"They feel their voices have not been
OL,8,Fheard and that there has been a
OL,9,Fbreakdown of trust between frontline
OL,10,Fstaff and senior management. That
OL,11,Frelationship must now be repaired.
OL,13,F"With Mr McBride and Dr Hill due
OL,14,Fbefore the Health Committee tomorrow,
OL,15,Falongside the new Chief Executive of
OL,16,Fthe Belfast Trust, I will be seeking
OL,17,Ffirm assurances that lessons are being
OL,18,Flearned, that decisive action will
OL,19,Ffollow, and that there is a credible
OL,20,Fplan to restore both public confidence
OL,21,Fand staff morale.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
