OL,3,CBelfast Trust culture report says
OL,4,Ccardiac unit poses risk to patient
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"I welcome the transparency this
OL,8,Freport brings - but that same openness
OL,9,Fmust now extend across all aspects of
OL,10,Fthe Trust's work, from patient care to
OL,11,Fcapital planning and future service
OL,12,Fdecisions."
OL,14,FBelfast Trust welcomes the publication
OL,15,Fof the McBride Hill Report. We look
OL,16,Fforward to developing an action plan
OL,17,Fand implementing the recommendations.
